title: Still (Cover)
lyrics:
“Still” is Billie Eilish’s cover of Ben Folds’s 2006 track, “Still”. Eilish posted the track onto her TikTok, on January 3, 2023.
[Verse 1]
I must give the impression
That I have the answers for everything
You were so disappointed
To see me unravel so easily
[Chorus]
It's only change
It's only everything I know
It's only change
And I'm only changing
